@UAV:CDC連測試的試劑都搞錯了，而且每天的測試量預計也衹有幾百份，更不要牢牢掌控測試資格，不開發地方實驗室的測試權<br>
The first testing kits from the Centers for Disease Control had a simple fault, and red tape prevented other labs from creating their own.<br>
